$ Oracle: Init parameter OPTIMIZER_REAL_TIME_STATISTICS
@ optimizer_real_time_statistics

If `optimizer_real_time_statistics` is set to `true`, Oracle will → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer/statistics/gathering/real-time[gather real time statistics] during conventional
→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/DML operations.

The default value is `false`.

The parameter is available in Oracle 19.10 and later.

